21e80978-9d0d-44a2-8f65-7441c2326f6e.title: General Wartface
21e80978-9d0d-44a2-8f65-7441c2326f6e.text:
You stupid! Only stupid goblins think red armour
better!

ee63e112-09b2-4973-ba50-f17165821b90.title: General Bentnoze
ee63e112-09b2-4973-ba50-f17165821b90.text: No they don't! Me think red armour better!

6a517838-2a4e-4a1f-918f-02a1c0af01be.title: General Wartface
6a517838-2a4e-4a1f-918f-02a1c0af01be.text: Then why you not like green armour?

c1b02258-e4bc-4f0d-aa34-fb56f504e73d.title: General Wartface
c1b02258-e4bc-4f0d-aa34-fb56f504e73d.text: Only stupid goblins think that! You stupid!

d49e76a4-ad24-4e72-bd2f-f6d483477940.title: General Wartface
d49e76a4-ad24-4e72-bd2f-f6d483477940.text: I tell all goblins in village to wear green armour now!

7a91b2a6-291e-4bcc-8be2-9639c7dc5501.title: General Bentnoze
7a91b2a6-291e-4bcc-8be2-9639c7dc5501.text:
They not listen to you! I already tell them wear red
armour!

175d6812-c0e8-4a73-a735-e95137625b98.title: General Wartface
175d6812-c0e8-4a73-a735-e95137625b98.text:
They listen to me not you! They know me bigger
general!

9eb564a2-f331-442a-93a9-840aae9961d1.title: General Bentnoze
9eb564a2-f331-442a-93a9-840aae9961d1.text: Me bigger general! They listen to me!

d8d36b6c-8402-4eb7-b125-e6a1790896a8.title: General Wartface
d8d36b6c-8402-4eb7-b125-e6a1790896a8.text: Human! What colour armour they wearing out there?

c0461b52-a42a-4060-ad9d-b9051582149e.title: <player>
c0461b52-a42a-4060-ad9d-b9051582149e.text: Half of them are wearing red and half of them green.

4c85414c-9d23-44b5-9b78-be3e28fa566b.title: General Bentnoze
4c85414c-9d23-44b5-9b78-be3e28fa566b.text:
Shut up human! They wearing green armour really!
Human lying because he scared of you!

8f1288be-8cae-42dc-b090-09bf25d6b61f.title: General Wartface
8f1288be-8cae-42dc-b090-09bf25d6b61f.text:
Human scared of me not you! Then you think me
bigger general!

c66e092f-b1f6-4323-b4a1-914831cfb3a8.title: General Wartface
c66e092f-b1f6-4323-b4a1-914831cfb3a8.text: No it has to be green!

f9a46108-8313-4e2e-8f1e-a35d4c9247e1.title: General Bentnoze
f9a46108-8313-4e2e-8f1e-a35d4c9247e1.text: All goblins should wear red armour!

34e3f0d9-f838-44e3-a1ed-8745f45ee1ea.title: General Wartface
34e3f0d9-f838-44e3-a1ed-8745f45ee1ea.text: Not red! Red armour make you look fat.

9a7c9b42-84af-4602-adae-eb1dd092c6c9.title: General Bentnoze
9a7c9b42-84af-4602-adae-eb1dd092c6c9.text: Even this human think you look fat! Don't you, human?

options.text: Why are you arguing about the colour of your armour?
Do you want me to pick an armour colour for you?

e261a107-73a3-44d7-96d4-1e7d383e5f71.title: <player>
e261a107-73a3-44d7-96d4-1e7d383e5f71.text:
Why are you arguing about the colour of your
armour?

448e3ab7-ce33-499a-a646-88e8a02c0b09.title: General Bentnoze
448e3ab7-ce33-499a-a646-88e8a02c0b09.text:
We decide to celebrate goblin new century by changing
colour of our armour, brown get boring after a bit. 
We want change.

e4feacbd-0c06-44a1-a0fe-9a157bdc6bef.title: General Wartface
e4feacbd-0c06-44a1-a0fe-9a157bdc6bef.text: Problem is they want different change to us.

7c7bcc4c-156c-4d9b-b1f8-c002ca4b0b30.title: General Wartface
7c7bcc4c-156c-4d9b-b1f8-c002ca4b0b30.text:
Yeah peace is good as long as it peace wearing green
armour.

ce016fcb-1a47-4688-b9e8-e3f3ad2a32ed.title: General Bentnoze
ce016fcb-1a47-4688-b9e8-e3f3ad2a32ed.text:
But green too much like skin. Nearly make you look
naked!

134be134-e3d6-4f1d-b0d7-7244127f38cd.title: General Bentnoze
134be134-e3d6-4f1d-b0d7-7244127f38cd.text: Ha ha! See, fatty? Even human think you fat!

a6b2f2de-b67d-4894-bb0e-3c383170ad5d.title: General Wartface
a6b2f2de-b67d-4894-bb0e-3c383170ad5d.text: Me not care what human think! Human ugly!

f1ef5e4e-2f6b-4ee3-a072-ec2a93516ae2.title: General Bentnoze
f1ef5e4e-2f6b-4ee3-a072-ec2a93516ae2.text: Shut up human! Wartface fat and human stupid!

83f2b821-51c2-400f-bf41-f847be4f8a22.title: <player>
83f2b821-51c2-400f-bf41-f847be4f8a22.text: Do you want me to pick an armour colour for you?

2d793b54-3990-4c98-8e6f-0679cdc86137.title: General Wartface
2d793b54-3990-4c98-8e6f-0679cdc86137.text: Yes as long as you pick green.

7c7c94f2-294a-4f3f-8cf0-fc2fbdc5bc65.title: General Bentnoze
7c7c94f2-294a-4f3f-8cf0-fc2fbdc5bc65.text: No you have to pick red!

a505d28e-6740-47c8-ae8d-dda5f91b04e4.title: General Bentnoze
a505d28e-6740-47c8-ae8d-dda5f91b04e4.text:
See? Even stupid human think red best. Now we all
wear red!

2286ba18-5b62-4414-9962-bf4ecfc3324e.title: General Wartface
2286ba18-5b62-4414-9962-bf4ecfc3324e.text:
Human not know anything! If we wear red then whole
village be ugly like YOU!

20fa9eb9-e53c-40cd-9a7b-6f0d1df89ae6.title: General Bentnoze
20fa9eb9-e53c-40cd-9a7b-6f0d1df89ae6.text: Go away human. You not helping.

1a1707c5-96b9-45a3-a770-9b11a41652b0.title: General Wartface
1a1707c5-96b9-45a3-a770-9b11a41652b0.text: Green! We all wear green now, human has decided!

50686446-9ae2-4b2d-b5d6-0b427c55859a.title: General Bentnoze
50686446-9ae2-4b2d-b5d6-0b427c55859a.text:
Why we have to do what human say? He not boss of
us!

ea0d6bf6-db54-471c-b364-e8b27d81d628.title: General Wartface
ea0d6bf6-db54-471c-b364-e8b27d81d628.text: No but he agree with me!

9e8e59df-dd3f-4259-ab81-50d07351bdc1.title: General Bentnoze
9e8e59df-dd3f-4259-ab81-50d07351bdc1.text: That prove you a filthy human-lover!

96af6c6f-35bb-4d10-80ed-d68d92f7cc23.title: General Wartface
96af6c6f-35bb-4d10-80ed-d68d92f7cc23.text: Me hate humans! This human just happen to be right!

3cdca971-1407-4573-b282-89498ab9d8be.title: General Bentnoze
3cdca971-1407-4573-b282-89498ab9d8be.text: Go away human. You not know anything.

9c12781b-e011-41c2-9c39-793f982a202b.title: <player>
9c12781b-e011-41c2-9c39-793f982a202b.text: What about a different colour? Not green or red?

148f3604-48d0-4cde-bfd2-b129ded4d85b.title: General Bentnoze
148f3604-48d0-4cde-bfd2-b129ded4d85b.text:
That would mean me wrong... but at least Wartface
not right!

57da39d6-6c84-4e8d-a4ed-f550b655e665.title: General Wartface
57da39d6-6c84-4e8d-a4ed-f550b655e665.text:
Me dunno what that look like. Have to see armour
before we decide.

00594372-819d-492f-afef-7184f9cdbb9d.title: General Bentnoze
00594372-819d-492f-afef-7184f9cdbb9d.text: Human! You bring us armour in new colour!

options.text: Why are you arguing about the colour of your armour?
I have some orange armour here.

e356a068-c1f0-4665-8514-bcab0552660e.title: <player>
e356a068-c1f0-4665-8514-bcab0552660e.text: I have some orange armour here.

c9f55182-d306-4dae-9fd5-7737416efe02.title: General Wartface
c9f55182-d306-4dae-9fd5-7737416efe02.text: No I don't like that much.

223d01f3-1216-4c98-8a10-0ca90a4ed53f.title: General Wartface
223d01f3-1216-4c98-8a10-0ca90a4ed53f.text: We need darker colour, like blue.

options.text: Why are you arguing about the colour of your armour?
I have some blue armour here.

611cc9f6-17a2-4b60-a7b0-bea5b94be73e.title: <player>
611cc9f6-17a2-4b60-a7b0-bea5b94be73e.text: I have some blue armour here.

3378bc69-20ab-4d58-a534-bff514a97572.title: General Bentnoze
3378bc69-20ab-4d58-a534-bff514a97572.text: That not right. Not goblin colour at all.

561945ca-3f2e-41a2-b5de-0c1d094d66e3.title: General Wartface
561945ca-3f2e-41a2-b5de-0c1d094d66e3.text: Goblins wear dark earthy colours like brown.

f64a59d7-df34-43a4-9865-7d194c19979c.title: <player>
f64a59d7-df34-43a4-9865-7d194c19979c.text:
I thought that was the armour you were changing
from. Never mind, anything is worth a try.

options.text: Why are you arguing about the colour of your armour?
I have some brown armour here.

99d3a10e-b408-4e23-9781-7b87646bb3b7.title: <player>
99d3a10e-b408-4e23-9781-7b87646bb3b7.text: I have some brown armour here.

26a87737-fd23-4a03-9ee6-7f640c2a4c80.title: General Wartface
26a87737-fd23-4a03-9ee6-7f640c2a4c80.text:
That colour quite nice. Me can see myself wearing
that.

01ecff13-2734-4978-b9b1-e932e94cd13f.title: General Bentnoze
01ecff13-2734-4978-b9b1-e932e94cd13f.text: It a deal then. Brown armour it is.

6f124fb0-0ed9-473e-8881-909a8b500a51.title: General Wartface
6f124fb0-0ed9-473e-8881-909a8b500a51.text:
Thank you for sorting out our argument. Take this
gold bar as reward!

aad18760-c641-4e61-ac49-d43c3880c5b7.title: Note
aad18760-c641-4e61-ac49-d43c3880c5b7.text: Missing dialogue if not returning with correct mail
